title: SPY Kicks-Off SoCal Cross Prestige Series
description: The Southern California Prestige Series of Cyclocross presented by SPY kicked-off this weekend in Downtown Los Angeles and the SPY Blue elite cycling team shattered the field in a 1,2,3 finish with SPY President Michael Marckx taking 2nd.
